### 상품 목록 조회 (PUBLIC) — 기본 최신순
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products

### 상품 목록 조회 — 브랜드 필터 + 가격순
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products?brandId=1&sort=price_asc&page=0&size=20

### 상품 목록 조회 — 좋아요 많은 순
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products?sort=likes_desc

---

### 상품 상세 조회 (PUBLIC)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/products/1

---

### 상품 목록 조회 (ADMIN)
GET http://localhost:8080/api-admin/v1/products
X-Loopers-Ldap: loopers.admin

---

### 상품 등록 (ADMIN) — 재고 함께 생성
POST http://localhost:8080/api-admin/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-Ldap: loopers.admin

{
  "name": "에어포스1",
  "price": 139000,
  "brandId": 1,
  "stockQuantity": 100
}

---

### 상품 수정 (ADMIN)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api-admin/v1/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-Ldap: loopers.admin

{
  "name": "에어포스1 화이트",
  "price": 149000
}

---

### 상품 삭제 (ADMIN)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api-admin/v1/products/1
X-Loopers-Ldap: loopers.admin

---

### 재고 수정 (ADMIN)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api-admin/v1/products/1/stock
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-Ldap: loopers.admin

{
  "quantity": 50
}
